@node REGISTER "HOW TO GET REGISTERED USER"

@{u}Registration@{uu}

As I said before, I declared all my tools as SHAREWARE, meaning that you
have to pay a registration fee to become the newest versions available.

The reason why I declare them as Shareware is simply...take a look to the
history-file, and you could see how many hard work i have done on this
tool...I don't believe that anyone will work simply for nothing, and there-
for I want money for my work.....

The Registration fee costs 30,-DM, and of course you have to pay this
only once ! After paying, you'll become access to my Register-Door, allowing
you to leech everytime the newest versions...I'll recommend to pay this,'coz
I will only release all of my programs one time, all other updates are only
for registered Users, including all userwishes and other things, which should
added to mEGA-vIEW or other tools comming from me.

To register yourself, call our @{"WHQ" LINK BBSADVERT1} and leave a mail to SieGeL/tRSi 
that you want to become registered User...

@endnode

