@node TODO "WHAT I PLANNED TO IMPLEMENT IN FUTURE RELEASES"

Some wishes are currently not implemented, coz this features are only for
registered Users...

- Better displaying of the contents from LHA/ZIP-archives, incl. date,bytes
  and other informations.

- Sysopcommands on LHA/ZIP - archives, allowing you to delete/add files.

- Downloading/Viewing more than only one file from an archive.

- Hydra-Support for Downloading

- Viewing of Guides in two ways, ANSI & GUIDE...:)

- maybe sometimes the support of the datatypes.library (WB/Kick 3.0+!)

- special Version for Tempest-BBS-Systems.

- better LZX-Handling like LHA & ZIP (Extracting, Downloading,etc.)

@endnode
